OL,3,CPubs to open longer if England or
OL,4,CScotland reach Euros 2024 semi-finals
OL,6,FPubs will be able to extend their
OL,7,Fopening hours to 1am if England or
OL,8,FScotland make it to the semi-finals of
OL,9,FEuro 2024, the government has said.
OL,11,FVenues will be allowed to stay open
OL,12,Ffor an extra two hours on match days
OL,13,Fif either or both teams reach the last
OL,14,Ffour ` or the final ` to give fans a
OL,15,Fchance to celebrate or commiserate.
OL,17,FThe move, which covers venues in
OL,18,FEngland and Wales, comes after a
OL,19,Fconsultation at the end of last year
OL,20,Fand is hoped to provide a boost to the
OL,21,Fhospitality industry.
