OL,3,CPubs to open longer if England or
OL,4,CScotland reach Euros 2024 semi-finals
OL,6,FHome Secretary James Cleverly said:
OL,7,F"We have listened to the public
OL,8,Fthrough our consultation and will be
OL,9,Fextending pub licensing hours should
OL,10,FEngland or Scotland reach the semi-
OL,11,Ffinals or final of Euro 2024."
OL,13,FHe added that the move will "allow
OL,14,Ffriends, families and communities to
OL,15,Fcome together for longer to watch
OL,16,Ftheir nation hopefully bring it home".
OL,18,FThe semi-finals are currently
OL,19,Fscheduled to take place on Tuesday
OL,20,FJuly 9 and Wednesday July 10, with the
OL,21,Ffinal taking place on Sunday July 14.
