OL,6,FThe head of trade body UK Hospitality,
OL,7,FKate Nicholls, said the extended hours
OL,8,Fwere "essential to allow venues and
OL,9,Ffans to take full advantage".
OL,11,FEmma McClarkin, chief executive of the
OL,12,FBritish Beer and Pub Association,
OL,13,Fsaid: "With the Euros fast
OL,14,Fapproaching, for many people there can
OL,15,Fbe no better place to cheer on their
OL,16,Fteam than with a refreshing beer at
OL,17,Ftheir local pub.
