OL,3,CPubs to open longer if England or
OL,4,CScotland reach Euros 2024 semi-finals
OL,6,F"It's great news that the Government
OL,7,Fhas anticipated the likely interest
OL,8,Ffrom pubs to keep their doors open a
OL,9,Flittle longer for the semi-finals and
OL,10,Ffinals during the European
OL,11,FChampionships."
OL,13,FEngland fell short of European glory
OL,14,Fin the final of the Covid-delayed Euro
OL,15,F2020 after losing to Italy in the
OL,16,Ffinal.
OL,18,FIf the team manages to go one better
OL,19,Fthis summer, it will be the first
OL,20,Fmajor trophy won by the country since
OL,21,Fthe World Cup in 1966.
