OL,3,CPubs to open longer if England or
OL,4,CScotland reach Euros 2024 semi-finals
OL,6,FThe government has previously pushed
OL,7,Fback pub closing times for royal
OL,8,Fweddings, the Queen's 90th birthday in
OL,9,F2016, the Fifa World Cup in 2014 and
OL,10,Fthe last Euro final in 2022.
OL,12,FThe Home Secretary, under Section 172
OL,13,Fof the Licensing Act 2003, can make an
OL,14,Forder relaxing licensing hours to mark
OL,15,Foccasions of "exceptional national
OL,16,Fsignificance".
