OL,6,FThe legislation will be laid in
OL,7,FParliament on Wednesday to ensure
OL,8,Fthere is enough time for it to be
OL,9,Fdebated and passed before the
OL,10,Ftournament begins.
OL,12,FA Scottish Government spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid it was up to local licensing
OL,14,Fboards whether or not to allow pubs to
OL,15,Fextend their opening hours.
